    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Investigative Journalism\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze an image from a news article and generate a headline.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Look at the images and articles already uploaded to this level or choose an image/article related to a recent news event.\r\n2. Start with a general prompt:\r\n\r\n>Write a headline for this image.\r\n\r\n3. Press **Send** and **review AI Chat's response**.\r\n4. **Refine your prompt** by providing **keywords** about the event in the image:\r\n\r\n>Write a headline for this image about a [movie/climate event/sports match].\r\n\r\n5. **Experiment**: \r\n   - Try different **keywords** or **phrasing** and compare how AI’s headlines change.\r\n   - What happens if the **keywords don't match the image** at all?\r\n   - **Upload a related PDF** (e.g., a news article, government report, or historical document). How does AI’s response change when it has additional text to analyze?\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**",
